      <p>A <a href="ch69s03.html#MonstersM-N11">medusa</a> is indistinguishable from a normal human at distances greater than 30 feet (or closer, if its face is concealed). The creature often wears garments that enhance its body while hiding its face behind a hood or veil.<a href="img/MonstersM-N.Medusa.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersM-N.Medusa.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A typical <a href="ch69s03.html#MonstersM-N11">medusa</a> is 5 to 6 feet tall and about the same weight as a human.</p>
      <p><a href="ch69s03.html#MonstersM-N11">Medusas</a> speak Common.</p>
